title: ERROR_ENCRYPTION_FAILED

title: ERROR_NO_USER_KEYS

title: ERROR_EFS_VERSION_NOT_SUPPORT

title: ERROR_CS_ENCRYPTION_INVALID_SERVER_RESPONSE

title: ERROR_CS_ENCRYPTION_UNSUPPORTED_SERVER

title: ERROR_CS_ENCRYPTION_EXISTING_ENCRYPTED_FILE

title: ERROR_CS_ENCRYPTION_NEW_ENCRYPTED_FILE

title: ERROR_CS_ENCRYPTION_FILE_NOT_CSE

title: ERROR_ENCRYPTION_POLICY_DENIES_OPERATION

title: ERROR_NO_BROWSER_SERVERS_FOUND

title: SCHED_E_SERVICE_NOT_LOCALSYSTEM

title: ERROR_LOG_SECTOR_INVALID

title: ERROR_LOG_SECTOR_PARITY_INVALID

title: ERROR_LOG_SECTOR_REMAPPED

title: ERROR_LOG_BLOCK_INCOMPLETE

title: ERROR_LOG_INVALID_RANGE

title: ERROR_LOG_BLOCKS_EXHAUSTED

title: ERROR_LOG_READ_CONTEXT_INVALID

title: ERROR_LOG_RESTART_INVALID
msg: Log service encountered an invalid log restart area.

title: ERROR_LOG_BLOCK_VERSION
msg: Log service encountered an invalid log block version.

title: ERROR_LOG_BLOCK_INVALID
msg: Log service encountered an invalid log block.

title: ERROR_LOG_READ_MODE_INVALID

title: ERROR_LOG_NO_RESTART
msg: Log service encountered a log stream with no restart area.

title: ERROR_LOG_METADATA_CORRUPT
msg: Log service encountered a corrupted metadata file.

title: ERROR_LOG_METADATA_INVALID

title: ERROR_LOG_METADATA_INCONSISTENT

title: ERROR_LOG_RESERVATION_INVALID

title: ERROR_LOG_CANT_DELETE
msg: Log service cannot delete log file or file system container.

title: ERROR_LOG_CONTAINER_LIMIT_EXCEEDED
msg: Log service has reached the maximum allowable containers allocated to a log file.

title: ERROR_LOG_START_OF_LOG
msg: Log service has attempted to read or write backward past the start of the log.

title: ERROR_LOG_POLICY_ALREADY_INSTALLED
msg: Log policy could not be installed because a policy of the same type is already present.

title: ERROR_LOG_POLICY_NOT_INSTALLED
msg: Log policy in question was not installed at the time of the request.

title: ERROR_LOG_POLICY_INVALID
msg: The installed set of policies on the log is invalid.

title: ERROR_LOG_POLICY_CONFLICT

title: ERROR_LOG_PINNED_ARCHIVE_TAIL
msg: Log space cannot be reclaimed because the log is pinned by the archive tail.

title: ERROR_LOG_RECORD_NONEXISTENT
msg: Log record is not a record in the log file.

title: ERROR_LOG_RECORDS_RESERVED_INVALID
msg: Number of reserved log records or the adjustment of the number of reserved log records is invalid.

title: ERROR_LOG_SPACE_RESERVED_INVALID
msg: Reserved log space or the adjustment of the log space is invalid.

title: ERROR_LOG_TAIL_INVALID
msg: An new or existing archive tail or base of the active log is invalid.

title: ERROR_LOG_FULL
msg: Log space is exhausted.

title: ERROR_COULD_NOT_RESIZE_LOG
msg: The log could not be set to the requested size.

title: ERROR_LOG_MULTIPLEXED
msg: Log is multiplexed, no direct writes to the physical log is allowed.

title: ERROR_LOG_DEDICATED
msg: The operation failed because the log is a dedicated log.

title: ERROR_LOG_ARCHIVE_NOT_IN_PROGRESS
msg: The operation requires an archive context.

title: ERROR_LOG_ARCHIVE_IN_PROGRESS
msg: Log archival is in progress.

title: ERROR_LOG_EPHEMERAL
msg: The operation requires a non-ephemeral log, but the log is ephemeral.

title: ERROR_LOG_NOT_ENOUGH_CONTAINERS
msg: The log must have at least two containers before it can be read from or written to.

title: ERROR_LOG_CLIENT_ALREADY_REGISTERED
msg: A log client has already registered on the stream.

title: ERROR_LOG_CLIENT_NOT_REGISTERED
msg: A log client has not been registered on the stream.

title: ERROR_LOG_FULL_HANDLER_IN_PROGRESS
msg: A request has already been made to handle the log full condition.

title: ERROR_LOG_CONTAINER_READ_FAILED
msg: Log service encountered an error when attempting to read from a log container.

title: ERROR_LOG_CONTAINER_WRITE_FAILED
msg: Log service encountered an error when attempting to write to a log container.

title: ERROR_LOG_CONTAINER_OPEN_FAILED
msg: Log service encountered an error when attempting open a log container.

title: ERROR_LOG_CONTAINER_STATE_INVALID
msg: Log service encountered an invalid container state when attempting a requested action.

title: ERROR_LOG_STATE_INVALID
msg: Log service is not in the correct state to perform a requested action.

title: ERROR_LOG_PINNED
msg: Log space cannot be reclaimed because the log is pinned.

title: ERROR_LOG_METADATA_FLUSH_FAILED
msg: Log metadata flush failed.

title: ERROR_LOG_INCONSISTENT_SECURITY
msg: Security on the log and its containers is inconsistent.

title: ERROR_LOG_APPENDED_FLUSH_FAILED
msg: Records were appended to the log or reservation changes were made, but the log could not be flushed.

title: ERROR_LOG_PINNED_RESERVATION
msg: The log is pinned due to reservation consuming most of the log space. Free some reserved records to make space available.

title: ERROR_INVALID_TRANSACTION
msg: The transaction handle associated with this operation is not valid.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_NOT_ACTIVE
msg: The requested operation was made in the context of a transaction that is no longer active.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_REQUEST_NOT_VALID
msg: The requested operation is not valid on the Transaction object in its current state.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_NOT_REQUESTED
msg: The caller has called a response API, but the response is not expected because the TM did not issue the corresponding request to the caller.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_ALREADY_ABORTED
msg: It is too late to perform the requested operation, since the Transaction has already been aborted.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_ALREADY_COMMITTED
msg: It is too late to perform the requested operation, since the Transaction has already been committed.

title: ERROR_TM_INITIALIZATION_FAILED
msg: The Transaction Manager was unable to be successfully initialized. Transacted operations are not supported.

title: ERROR_RESOURCEMANAGER_READ_ONLY
msg: The specified ResourceManager made no changes or updates to the resource under this transaction.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_NOT_JOINED
msg: The resource manager has attempted to prepare a transaction that it has not successfully joined.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_SUPERIOR_EXISTS
msg: The Transaction object already has a superior enlistment, and the caller attempted an operation that would have created a new superior. Only a single superior enlistment is allow.

title: ERROR_CRM_PROTOCOL_ALREADY_EXISTS
msg: The RM tried to register a protocol that already exists.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_PROPAGATION_FAILED
msg: The attempt to propagate the Transaction failed.

title: ERROR_CRM_PROTOCOL_NOT_FOUND
msg: The requested propagation protocol was not registered as a CRM.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_INVALID_MARSHALL_BUFFER
msg: The buffer passed in to PushTransaction or PullTransaction is not in a valid format.

title: ERROR_CURRENT_TRANSACTION_NOT_VALID
msg: The current transaction context associated with the thread is not a valid handle to a transaction object.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_NOT_FOUND
msg: The specified Transaction object could not be opened, because it was not found.

title: ERROR_RESOURCEMANAGER_NOT_FOUND
msg: The specified ResourceManager object could not be opened, because it was not found.

title: ERROR_ENLISTMENT_NOT_FOUND
msg: The specified Enlistment object could not be opened, because it was not found.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTIONMANAGER_NOT_FOUND
msg: The specified TransactionManager object could not be opened, because it was not found.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTIONMANAGER_NOT_ONLINE
msg: The object specified could not be created or opened, because its associated TransactionManager is not online. The TransactionManager must be brought fully Online by calling RecoverTransactionManager to recover to the end of its LogFile before objects in its Transaction or ResourceManager namespaces can be opened. In addition, errors in writing records to its LogFile can cause a TransactionManager to go offline.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTIONMANAGER_RECOVERY_NAME_COLLISION
msg: The specified TransactionManager was unable to create the objects contained in its logfile in the Ob namespace. Therefore, the TransactionManager was unable to recover.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_NOT_ROOT
msg: The call to create a superior Enlistment on this Transaction object could not be completed, because the Transaction object specified for the enlistment is a subordinate branch of the Transaction. Only the root of the Transaction can be enlisted on as a superior.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_OBJECT_EXPIRED
msg: Because the associated transaction manager or resource manager has been closed, the handle is no longer valid.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_RESPONSE_NOT_ENLISTED
msg: The specified operation could not be performed on this Superior enlistment, because the enlistment was not created with the corresponding completion response in the NotificationMask.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_RECORD_TOO_LONG
msg: The specified operation could not be performed, because the record that would be logged was too long. This can occur because of two conditions: either there are too many Enlistments on this Transaction, or the combined RecoveryInformation being logged on behalf of those Enlistments is too long.

title: ERROR_IMPLICIT_TRANSACTION_NOT_SUPPORTED
msg: Implicit transaction are not supported.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_INTEGRITY_VIOLATED
msg: The kernel transaction manager had to abort or forget the transaction because it blocked forward progress.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTIONMANAGER_IDENTITY_MISMATCH
msg: The TransactionManager identity that was supplied did not match the one recorded in the TransactionManager's log file.

title: ERROR_RM_CANNOT_BE_FROZEN_FOR_SNAPSHOT
msg: This snapshot operation cannot continue because a transactional resource manager cannot be frozen in its current state. Please try again.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_MUST_WRITETHROUGH
msg: The transaction cannot be enlisted on with the specified EnlistmentMask, because the transaction has already completed the PrePrepare phase. In order to ensure correctness, the ResourceManager must switch to a write- through mode and cease caching data within this transaction. Enlisting for only subsequent transaction phases may still succeed.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_NO_SUPERIOR
msg: The transaction does not have a superior enlistment.

title: ERROR_HEURISTIC_DAMAGE_POSSIBLE
msg: The attempt to commit the Transaction completed, but it is possible that some portion of the transaction tree did not commit successfully due to heuristics. Therefore it is possible that some data modified in the transaction may not have committed, resulting in transactional inconsistency. If possible, check the consistency of the associated data.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTIONAL_CONFLICT
msg: The function attempted to use a name that is reserved for use by another transaction.

title: ERROR_RM_NOT_ACTIVE
msg: Transaction support within the specified resource manager is not started or was shut down due to an error.

title: ERROR_RM_METADATA_CORRUPT
msg: The metadata of the RM has been corrupted. The RM will not function.

title: ERROR_DIRECTORY_NOT_RM
msg: The specified directory does not contain a resource manager.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTIONS_UNSUPPORTED_REMOTE
msg: The remote server or share does not support transacted file operations.

title: ERROR_LOG_RESIZE_INVALID_SIZE
msg: The requested log size is invalid.

title: ERROR_OBJECT_NO_LONGER_EXISTS
msg: The object (file, stream, link) corresponding to the handle has been deleted by a Transaction Savepoint Rollback.

title: ERROR_STREAM_MINIVERSION_NOT_FOUND
msg: The specified file miniversion was not found for this transacted file open.

title: ERROR_STREAM_MINIVERSION_NOT_VALID
msg: The specified file miniversion was found but has been invalidated. Most likely cause is a transaction savepoint rollback.

title: ERROR_MINIVERSION_INACCESSIBLE_FROM_SPECIFIED_TRANSACTION
msg: A miniversion may only be opened in the context of the transaction that created it.

title: ERROR_CANT_OPEN_MINIVERSION_WITH_MODIFY_INTENT
msg: It is not possible to open a miniversion with modify access.

title: ERROR_CANT_CREATE_MORE_STREAM_MINIVERSIONS
msg: It is not possible to create any more miniversions for this stream.

title: ERROR_REMOTE_FILE_VERSION_MISMATCH
msg: The remote server sent mismatching version number or Fid for a file opened with transactions.

title: ERROR_HANDLE_NO_LONGER_VALID
msg: The handle has been invalidated by a transaction. The most likely cause is the presence of memory mapping on a file or an open handle when the transaction ended or rolled back to savepoint.

title: ERROR_NO_TXF_METADATA
msg: There is no transaction metadata on the file.

title: ERROR_LOG_CORRUPTION_DETECTED
msg: The log data is corrupt.

title: ERROR_CANT_RECOVER_WITH_HANDLE_OPEN
msg: The file can't be recovered because there is a handle still open on it.

title: ERROR_RM_DISCONNECTED
msg: The transaction outcome is unavailable because the resource manager responsible for it has disconnected.

title: ERROR_ENLISTMENT_NOT_SUPERIOR
msg: The request was rejected because the enlistment in question is not a superior enlistment.

title: ERROR_RECOVERY_NOT_NEEDED
msg: The transactional resource manager is already consistent. Recovery is not needed.

title: ERROR_RM_ALREADY_STARTED
msg: The transactional resource manager has already been started.

title: ERROR_FILE_IDENTITY_NOT_PERSISTENT
msg: The file cannot be opened transactionally, because its identity depends on the outcome of an unresolved transaction.

title: ERROR_CANT_BREAK_TRANSACTIONAL_DEPENDENCY
msg: The operation cannot be performed because another transaction is depending on the fact that this property will not change.

title: ERROR_CANT_CROSS_RM_BOUNDARY
msg: The operation would involve a single file with two transactional resource managers and is therefore not allowed.

title: ERROR_TXF_DIR_NOT_EMPTY
msg: The $Txf directory must be empty for this operation to succeed.

title: ERROR_INDOUBT_TRANSACTIONS_EXIST
msg: The operation would leave a transactional resource manager in an inconsistent state and is therefore not allowed.

title: ERROR_TM_VOLATILE
msg: The operation could not be completed because the transaction manager does not have a log.

title: ERROR_ROLLBACK_TIMER_EXPIRED
msg: A rollback could not be scheduled because a previously scheduled rollback has already executed or been queued for execution.

title: ERROR_TXF_ATTRIBUTE_CORRUPT
msg: The transactional metadata attribute on the file or directory is corrupt and unreadable.

title: ERROR_EFS_NOT_ALLOWED_IN_TRANSACTION
msg: The encryption operation could not be completed because a transaction is active.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTIONAL_OPEN_NOT_ALLOWED
msg: This object is not allowed to be opened in a transaction.

title: ERROR_LOG_GROWTH_FAILED
msg: An attempt to create space in the transactional resource manager's log failed. The failure status has been recorded in the event log.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTED_MAPPING_UNSUPPORTED_REMOTE
msg: Memory mapping (creating a mapped section) a remote file under a transaction is not supported.

title: ERROR_TXF_METADATA_ALREADY_PRESENT
msg: Transaction metadata is already present on this file and cannot be superseded.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_SCOPE_CALLBACKS_NOT_SET
msg: A transaction scope could not be entered because the scope handler has not been initialized.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_REQUIRED_PROMOTION
msg: Promotion was required in order to allow the resource manager to enlist, but the transaction was set to disallow it.

title: ERROR_CANNOT_EXECUTE_FILE_IN_TRANSACTION
msg: This file is open for modification in an unresolved transaction and may be opened for execute only by a transacted reader.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTIONS_NOT_FROZEN
msg: The request to thaw frozen transactions was ignored because transactions had not previously been frozen.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_FREEZE_IN_PROGRESS
msg: Transactions cannot be frozen because a freeze is already in progress.

title: ERROR_NOT_SNAPSHOT_VOLUME
msg: The target volume is not a snapshot volume. This operation is only valid on a volume mounted as a snapshot.

title: ERROR_NO_SAVEPOINT_WITH_OPEN_FILES
msg: The savepoint operation failed because files are open on the transaction. This is not permitted.

title: ERROR_DATA_LOST_REPAIR
msg: Windows has discovered corruption in a file, and that file has since been repaired. Data loss may have occurred.

title: ERROR_SPARSE_NOT_ALLOWED_IN_TRANSACTION
msg: The sparse operation could not be completed because a transaction is active on the file.

title: ERROR_TM_IDENTITY_MISMATCH
msg: The call to create a TransactionManager object failed because the Tm Identity stored in the logfile does not match the Tm Identity that was passed in as an argument.

title: ERROR_FLOATED_SECTION
msg: I/O was attempted on a section object that has been floated as a result of a transaction ending. There is no valid data.

title: ERROR_CANNOT_ACCEPT_TRANSACTED_WORK
msg: The transactional resource manager cannot currently accept transacted work due to a transient condition such as low resources.

title: ERROR_CANNOT_ABORT_TRANSACTIONS
msg: The transactional resource manager had too many tranactions outstanding that could not be aborted. The transactional resource manger has been shut down.

title: ERROR_BAD_CLUSTERS
msg: The operation could not be completed due to bad clusters on disk.

title: ERROR_COMPRESSION_NOT_ALLOWED_IN_TRANSACTION
msg: The compression operation could not be completed because a transaction is active on the file.

title: ERROR_VOLUME_DIRTY
msg: The operation could not be completed because the volume is dirty. Please run chkdsk and try again.

title: ERROR_NO_LINK_TRACKING_IN_TRANSACTION
msg: The link tracking operation could not be completed because a transaction is active.

title: ERROR_OPERATION_NOT_SUPPORTED_IN_TRANSACTION
msg: This operation cannot be performed in a transaction.

title: ERROR_EXPIRED_HANDLE
msg: The handle is no longer properly associated with its transaction. It may have been opened in a transactional resource manager that was subsequently forced to restart. Please close the handle and open a new one.

title: ERROR_TRANSACTION_NOT_ENLISTED
msg: The specified operation could not be performed because the resource manager is not enlisted in the transaction.

title: ERROR_CTX_WINSTATION_NAME_INVALID
msg: The specified session name is invalid.

title: ERROR_CTX_INVALID_PD
msg: The specified protocol driver is invalid.

title: ERROR_CTX_PD_NOT_FOUND
msg: The specified protocol driver was not found in the system path.

title: ERROR_CTX_WD_NOT_FOUND
msg: The specified terminal connection driver was not found in the system path.

title: ERROR_CTX_CANNOT_MAKE_EVENTLOG_ENTRY
msg: A registry key for event logging could not be created for this session.

title: ERROR_CTX_SERVICE_NAME_COLLISION
msg: A service with the same name already exists on the system.

title: ERROR_CTX_CLOSE_PENDING
msg: A close operation is pending on the session.

title: ERROR_CTX_NO_OUTBUF
msg: There are no free output buffers available.

title: ERROR_CTX_MODEM_INF_NOT_FOUND
msg: The MODEM.INF file was not found.

title: ERROR_CTX_INVALID_MODEMNAME
msg: The modem name was not found in MODEM.INF.

title: ERROR_CTX_MODEM_RESPONSE_ERROR
msg: The modem did not accept the command sent to it. Verify that the configured modem name matches the attached modem.

title: ERROR_CTX_MODEM_RESPONSE_TIMEOUT
msg: The modem did not respond to the command sent to it. Verify that the modem is properly cabled and powered on.

title: ERROR_CTX_MODEM_RESPONSE_NO_CARRIER
msg: Carrier detect has failed or carrier has been dropped due to disconnect.

title: ERROR_CTX_MODEM_RESPONSE_NO_DIALTONE
msg: Dial tone not detected within the required time. Verify that the phone cable is properly attached and functional.

title: ERROR_CTX_MODEM_RESPONSE_BUSY
msg: Busy signal detected at remote site on callback.

title: ERROR_CTX_MODEM_RESPONSE_VOICE
msg: Voice detected at remote site on callback.

title: ERROR_CTX_TD_ERROR
msg: Transport driver error.

title: ERROR_CTX_WINSTATION_NOT_FOUND
msg: The specified session cannot be found.

title: ERROR_CTX_WINSTATION_ALREADY_EXISTS
msg: The specified session name is already in use.

title: ERROR_CTX_WINSTATION_BUSY
msg: The task you are trying to do can't be completed because Remote Desktop Services is currently busy. Please try again in a few minutes. Other users should still be able to log on.

title: ERROR_CTX_BAD_VIDEO_MODE
msg: An attempt has been made to connect to a session whose video mode is not supported by the current client.

title: ERROR_CTX_GRAPHICS_INVALID
msg: The application attempted to enable DOS graphics mode. DOS graphics mode is not supported.

title: ERROR_CTX_LOGON_DISABLED
msg: Your interactive logon privilege has been disabled. Please contact your administrator.

title: ERROR_CTX_NOT_CONSOLE
msg: The requested operation can be performed only on the system console. This is most often the result of a driver or system DLL requiring direct console access.

title: ERROR_CTX_CLIENT_QUERY_TIMEOUT
msg: The client failed to respond to the server connect message.

title: ERROR_CTX_CONSOLE_DISCONNECT
msg: Disconnecting the console session is not supported.

title: ERROR_CTX_CONSOLE_CONNECT
msg: Reconnecting a disconnected session to the console is not supported.

title: ERROR_CTX_SHADOW_DENIED
msg: The request to control another session remotely was denied.

title: ERROR_CTX_WINSTATION_ACCESS_DENIED
msg: The requested session access is denied.

title: ERROR_CTX_INVALID_WD
msg: The specified terminal connection driver is invalid.

title: ERROR_CTX_SHADOW_INVALID
msg: The requested session cannot be controlled remotely. This may be because the session is disconnected or does not currently have a user logged on.

title: ERROR_CTX_SHADOW_DISABLED
msg: The requested session is not configured to allow remote control.

title: ERROR_CTX_CLIENT_LICENSE_IN_USE
msg: Your request to connect to this Terminal Server has been rejected. Your Terminal Server client license number is currently being used by another user. Please call your system administrator to obtain a unique license number.

title: ERROR_CTX_CLIENT_LICENSE_NOT_SET
msg: Your request to connect to this Terminal Server has been rejected. Your Terminal Server client license number has not been entered for this copy of the Terminal Server client. Please contact your system administrator.

title: ERROR_CTX_LICENSE_NOT_AVAILABLE
msg: The number of connections to this computer is limited and all connections are in use right now. Try connecting later or contact your system administrator.

title: ERROR_CTX_LICENSE_CLIENT_INVALID
msg: The client you are using is not licensed to use this system. Your logon request is denied.

title: ERROR_CTX_LICENSE_EXPIRED
msg: The system license has expired. Your logon request is denied.

title: ERROR_CTX_SHADOW_NOT_RUNNING
msg: Remote control could not be terminated because the specified session is not currently being remotely controlled.

title: ERROR_CTX_SHADOW_ENDED_BY_MODE_CHANGE
msg: The remote control of the console was terminated because the display mode was changed. Changing the display mode in a remote control session is not supported.

title: ERROR_ACTIVATION_COUNT_EXCEEDED
msg: Activation has already been reset the maximum number of times for this installation. Your activation timer will not be cleared.

title: ERROR_CTX_WINSTATIONS_DISABLED
msg: Remote logins are currently disabled.

title: ERROR_CTX_ENCRYPTION_LEVEL_REQUIRED
msg: You do not have the proper encryption level to access this Session.

title: ERROR_CTX_SESSION_IN_USE
msg: The user %s\\%s is currently logged on to this computer. Only the current user or an administrator can log on to this computer.

title: ERROR_CTX_NO_FORCE_LOGOFF
msg: The user %s\\%s is already logged on to the console of this computer. You do not have permission to log in at this time. To resolve this issue, contact %s\\%s and have them log off.

title: ERROR_CTX_ACCOUNT_RESTRICTION
msg: Unable to log you on because of an account restriction.

title: ERROR_RDP_PROTOCOL_ERROR
msg: The RDP protocol component %2 detected an error in the protocol stream and has disconnected the client.

title: ERROR_CTX_CDM_CONNECT
msg: The Client Drive Mapping Service Has Connected on Terminal Connection.

title: ERROR_CTX_CDM_DISCONNECT
msg: The Client Drive Mapping Service Has Disconnected on Terminal Connection.

title: ERROR_CTX_SECURITY_LAYER_ERROR
msg: The Terminal Server security layer detected an error in the protocol stream and has disconnected the client.

title: ERROR_TS_INCOMPATIBLE_SESSIONS
msg: The target session is incompatible with the current session.

title: ERROR_TS_VIDEO_SUBSYSTEM_ERROR
msg: Windows can't connect to your session because a problem occurred in the Windows video subsystem. Try connecting again later, or contact the server administrator for assistance.

title: FRS_ERR_INVALID_API_SEQUENCE
msg: The file replication service API was called incorrectly.

title: FRS_ERR_STARTING_SERVICE
msg: The file replication service cannot be started.

title: FRS_ERR_STOPPING_SERVICE
msg: The file replication service cannot be stopped.

title: FRS_ERR_INTERNAL_API
msg: The file replication service API terminated the request. The event log may have more information.

title: FRS_ERR_INTERNAL
msg: The file replication service terminated the request. The event log may have more information.

title: FRS_ERR_SERVICE_COMM
msg: The file replication service cannot be contacted. The event log may have more information.

title: FRS_ERR_INSUFFICIENT_PRIV

title: FRS_ERR_AUTHENTICATION
msg: The file replication service cannot satisfy the request because authenticated RPC is not available. The event log may have more information.

title: FRS_ERR_PARENT_INSUFFICIENT_PRIV
msg: The file replication service cannot satisfy the request because the user has insufficient privileges on the domain controller. The event log may have more information.

title: FRS_ERR_PARENT_AUTHENTICATION
msg: The file replication service cannot satisfy the request because authenticated RPC is not available on the domain controller. The event log may have more information.

title: FRS_ERR_CHILD_TO_PARENT_COMM

title: FRS_ERR_PARENT_TO_CHILD_COMM

title: FRS_ERR_SYSVOL_POPULATE
msg: The file replication service cannot populate the system volume because of an internal error. The event log may have more information.

title: FRS_ERR_SYSVOL_POPULATE_TIMEOUT
msg: The file replication service cannot populate the system volume because of an internal timeout. The event log may have more information.

title: FRS_ERR_SYSVOL_IS_BUSY
msg: The file replication service cannot process the request. The system volume is busy with a previous request.

title: FRS_ERR_SYSVOL_DEMOTE
msg: The file replication service cannot stop replicating the system volume because of an internal error. The event log may have more information.

title: FRS_ERR_INVALID_SERVICE_PARAMETER
msg: The file replication service detected an invalid parameter.
